</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"d33b7985f98c569e153b9bc4a0dd938611365f99","tid":385181,"uid":142725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"大家支唔支持我開個無廣告嘅新登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：it狗"},{"pid":"8b353f830f95d9df3154f97b36ed5a803ea4260f","tid":385181,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀"},{"pid":"c547db8f0f1da033428529b0f632672400caf7bc","tid":385181,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d 打手好低級，次次都話你有本事就開個新壇，同五毛話唔鐘意香港可以去別國一樣。連尼住呢個人陰險貪財就一定係。連登討論低質亦大家同意。<br />\n<br />\n大家去番高登好過喇，當日話高登點差點差，我屌你老母連登學太陸微博秒速刪post又唔敢講。<br />\n<br />\n番高登喇，只少早洩個人簡單無機心，有機心會開放api俾你賺錢上位，你連仆街提都唔敢提個api俾人，怕自己做剃頭者俾人吸走人，想壟斷曬賺錢。食屎狗。</blockquote><br />\n哦 係呀 我係打手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cd6efc7dabad93cdb955d7f33b025a5c060f47","tid":385181,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家支唔支持我開個無廣告嘅新登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：it狗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26a3c140f67c2be2242881a4194599734ea97e1","tid":385181,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"Agger"}]}